caption:
🌅✨ “Chasing sunsets, capturing memories.”
Luna, 23, stands on a cliff above the turquoise sea of Sofija, Croatia, crop top and shorts fluttering in the golden hour breeze. Her hair flows as her eyes sparkle, DSLR in hand, capturing the perfect moment while her friend and a golden retriever enjoy the view beside her. Mountains, beach, and cinematic sunlight make every frame unforgettable. 📸🐾
